OL,3,CWarmest May and spring on record in
OL,4,CUK, Met Office figures show
OL,6,FThe UK had its warmest May and spring
OL,7,Fon record, despite the wet, dull
OL,8,Fconditions for many parts of the
OL,9,Fcountry, provisional Met Office
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FMay 2024 recorded an average
OL,13,Ftemperature of 13.1C for the UK,
OL,14,Fbeating the previous record in 2008 by
OL,15,Fa full 1C, making it the warmest May
OL,16,Fin records dating back to 1884.
