OL,6,FThe Met Office said the month's high
OL,7,Faverage temperatures were influenced
OL,8,Fparticularly by warm conditions in the
OL,9,Fnorthern half of the UK, and by high
OL,10,Fovernight temperatures.
OL,12,FMeteorological spring, which covers
OL,13,Fthe months of March, April and May,
OL,14,Fwas also the warmest on record, the
OL,15,Ffigures show.
