OL,3,CWarmest May and spring on record in
OL,4,CUK, Met Office figures show
OL,6,FA Met Office spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Higher than average temperatures in
OL,8,FMarch and May, either side of a
OL,9,Fslightly warmer than average April,
OL,10,Fmeans that spring 2024 is the warmest
OL,11,Fon record according to mean
OL,12,Ftemperature.
OL,14,F"Despite the warmth, sunshine hours
OL,15,Fduring the season were well below
OL,16,Faverage, though not troubling any
OL,17,Fnational records.
